{"tid":1742370,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"反思投票嘅意義","createTime":"2019-11-20T18:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T23:58:51.000Z","uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"488475affff4d18111c33312417de8d6797705b2","tid":1742370,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:30:17.000Z","msg":"剛剛睇到一個youtuber講區選嘅意見<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ajE1lfcLQr8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FajE1lfcLQr8&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=986c17e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ajE1lfcLQr8</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然對於公海來講，呢條片所講嘅對某部份巴絲來講真係好難接受，特別係認為票投泛民令建制輸得一敗塗地嘅巴絲來講，直頭係大大巴摑落去佢地塊面度，但係如果唔咁做，繼續保持呢個諗法嘅人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都廢事畀。<br />\n當然我作度選民，我有票都點都要投咗先，但係心態上就要改一改，唔好講到冇區選/立選都會係世界末日咁。"},{"pid":"ad30197a385c2d22658e86eb66fed407c8a2cd79","tid":1742370,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T23:58:51.000Z","msg":"極度同意"}]}